OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784294319
OL,3,CConcerns over patient safety after
OL,4,Ctech issue with hospital letters
OL,6,FMore than 7,000 hospital discharge
OL,7,Fletters may not have been received by
OL,8,FGP practices across Jersey, the
OL,9,Fisland's Health Minister has revealed.
OL,11,FSenator Tom Binet says an issue with a
OL,12,Fthird-party computer system has been
OL,13,Fdiscovered, meaning letters sent
OL,14,Felectronically by healthcare staff at
OL,15,Fthe General Hospital from February
OL,16,Fonwards may not have been received by
OL,17,FGPs.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
