FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784294319
OL,3,CConcerns over patient safety after
OL,4,Ctech issue with hospital letters
OL,6,FThese documents are a summary of
OL,7,Fsomeone's stay in hospital and detail
OL,8,Fimportant information about why they
OL,9,Fattended, what treatment was given,
OL,10,Fincluding any medicine changes, and
OL,11,Fwhether any further care, tests or
OL,12,Freferrals are needed.
OL,14,FOne retired doctor has told ITV
OL,15,FChannel this issue is significant
OL,16,Fbecause patients could be directly
OL,17,Fimpacted by missing repeat
OL,18,Fprescriptions and follow-up treatment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784294319
OL,3,CConcerns over patient safety after
OL,4,Ctech issue with hospital letters
OL,6,FHowever, the letters have not been
OL,7,Flost and Senator Binet says "work is
OL,8,Funderway to make sure GP practices
OL,9,Freceive the information they need".
OL,11,FHe has apologised and they believe
OL,12,Fmore than a quarter of hospital
OL,13,Fdischarge letters sent since February
OL,14,Fmay be affected.
OL,16,FSenator Binet adds: "Health department
OL,17,Fstaff and GPs are working closely
OL,18,Ftogether to resolve the issue and
OL,19,Freview any impact on patients.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784294319
OL,3,CConcerns over patient safety after
OL,4,Ctech issue with hospital letters
OL,6,F"The issue is with third-party
OL,7,Fsoftware which links the hospital and
OL,8,FGP computer systems. It is not an
OL,9,Ferror in either the hospital or GP
OL,10,Felectronic patient record systems.
OL,12,F"GP practices will receive a report
OL,13,Ftomorrow, Thursday 16 July, to help
OL,14,Fthem identify any patients who may
OL,15,Fhave been affected.
OL,17,F"GPs will review this information and,
OL,18,Fif they have any concerns about your
OL,19,Fcare, they will contact you directly.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784294319
OL,3,CConcerns over patient safety after
OL,4,Ctech issue with hospital letters
OL,6,F"Islanders do not need to take any
OL,7,Faction at this stage."
OL,9,FPaper discharge letters are now being
OL,10,Fproduced in the Emergency Department
OL,11,Fso patients have a copy when they
OL,12,Fleave.
OL,14,FSenator Binet explains: "This issue
OL,15,Fhighlights the importance of improving
OL,16,Fdigital systems across health and
OL,17,Fsocial care, and why investment is
OL,18,Fbeing made to improve the sharing of
OL,19,Fmedical information safely and
OL,20,Freliably.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784294319
OL,3,CConcerns over patient safety after
OL,4,Ctech issue with hospital letters
OL,6,F"We apologise for any concern this may
OL,7,Fcause. We are working as quickly as
OL,8,Fpossible to restore fully reliable
OL,9,Flinks and ensure that GP practices
OL,10,Fconsistently receive electronic
OL,11,Fdischarge summaries."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
